                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>By exchange of notes signed at Tegucigalpa, January 22, March 20, and April 23,
                    1952, and entered into force on the latter date, the United States and Honduras
                    concluded a Military Air Transit Agreement; for text, see Department of State
                    Treaties and Other International Acts Series (TIAS) No. 2502, or <hi
                        rend="italic">United States Treaties and Other International Agreements</hi>
                    (UST), volume 3 (pt. 3), page 3734.</p>
            </div>
